sink-after-revenue-warning-2024-01-09/</link><description>英国牛津纳米孔公司(Oxford Nanopore)周二发布收入预警，称其股价下跌近12%，原因是中国和中东经济放缓，以及大客户的交错采购。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:01:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/britains-oxford-nanopores-shares-sink-after-revenue-warning-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车品牌通过电动汽车升级提高盈利能力-瑞银</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-auto-brands-improve-profitability-with-ev-upgrades-ubs-2024-01-09/</link><description>瑞银分析师周二表示，尽管全球最大汽车市场的竞争加剧，但由于中国汽车品牌不断升级电动汽车（EV）产品组合，中国汽车品牌预计将在 2024 年实现更好的盈利能力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 09:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-auto-brands-improve-profitability-with-ev-upgrades-ubs-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国卫星发射在关键投票前引发台湾警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-says-chinese-satellite-flies-over-south-taiwan-airspace-2024-01-09/</link><description>台湾政府周二向全岛范围发出警报，称一颗中国卫星飞越其南部领空，台湾外交部长称这是关键选举前几天骚扰行为的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-says-chinese-satellite-flies-over-south-taiwan-airspace-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>对冲基金质疑债务比率后，西班牙制药商 Grifols 股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/short-seller-gotham-city-questions-grifols-debt-ratios-2024-01-09/</link><description>西班牙制药公司 Grifols 的股价周二暴跌逾 40%，此前对冲基金 Gotham City Research 声称其债务比率约为官方报告的两倍。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:22:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/short-seller-gotham-city-questions-grifols-debt-ratios-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>桥梁困境凸显台湾选举中对中国的分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bridge-dilemma-captures-divide-over-china-taiwan-elections-2024-01-09/</link><description>陈沧江指着办公室一水之隔的厦门摩天大楼，回忆起30年前这座中国南方城市和台湾金门岛一样低矮的情况。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:18:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bridge-dilemma-captures-divide-over-china-taiwan-elections-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>印尼准备与各国合作敲定南海法规</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-ready-work-with-countries-finalise-south-china-sea-code-2024-01-09/</link><description>印度尼西亚外交部长蕾特诺·马尔苏迪周二表示，印度尼西亚准备与其他东南亚国家合作，敲定拖延已久的南海行为准则，该国许多邻国与中国在南海存在重叠的主权声索。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 06:55:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-ready-work-with-countries-finalise-south-china-sea-code-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>经济疲软、新冠疫情肆虐可能导致2023年中国人口再次减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/weak-economy-covid-rampage-likely-shrank-chinas-population-again-2023-2024-01-09/</link><description>由于中国突然结束严格的封锁，与新冠病毒相关的死亡人数激增，2023年中国人口可能连续第二年下降，而对经济前景的信心疲弱导致出生率低迷。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 06:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/weak-economy-covid-rampage-likely-shrank-chinas-population-again-2023-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着印度关系恶化，马尔代夫总统吸引中国投资者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-president-courts-investors-china-ties-with-india-sag-2024-01-09/</link><description>在中国南部港口城市举行的“投资马尔代夫”论坛上，马尔代夫总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖与面带微笑的当地官员握手并交谈，此次中国之行旨在深化双边关系，因为这个群岛国家正在远离印度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 05:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-president-courts-investors-china-ties-with-india-sag-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪将于下周在印度尼西亚推出汽车 - 公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launch-cars-indonesia-next-week-company-2024-01-09/</link><description>中国比亚迪公司周二表示，全球最大的纯电动汽车 (BEV) 销售商将于下周在印度尼西亚推出其汽车。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 05:28:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launch-cars-indonesia-next-week-company-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>香港领导人表示国泰航空需要解决运力问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-needs-address-capacity-issues-hong-kong-leader-says-2024-01-09/</link><description>香港领导人表示，香港国泰航空计划在繁忙的农历新年期间削减航班，这表明该航空公司需要解决运力问题，而其飞行员工会则呼吁政府进行调查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:22:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-needs-address-capacity-issues-hong-kong-leader-says-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 所有者字节跳动正在与腾讯等公司洽谈出售游戏资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tiktok-owner-bytedance-talks-with-tencent-others-sell-gaming-assets-2024-01-09/</link><description>TikTok 母公司字节跳动周二表示，随着这家中国社交媒体公司退出游戏行业，该公司正在与其游戏资产的多个潜在买家进行谈判，其中包括全球最大的视频游戏公司腾讯。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 02:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tiktok-owner-bytedance-talks-with-tencent-others-sell-gaming-assets-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国在大选前向台湾施加压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ruling-party-candidate-will-maintain-status-quo-engage-with-china-2024-01-09/</link><description>中国周二威胁对台湾采取新的贸易措施，在周末选举前施加压力，台北抱怨更多中国气球，执政党总统候选人警告不要与北京“假和平”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 01:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ruling-party-candidate-will-maintain-status-quo-engage-with-china-2024-01-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>